	 public static String  sp_Block03_HeadingD02="     2.  Only end to end, GN quota bookings will be applicable.";
	 public static String  sp_Block03_HeadingD03="     3.  Cancellation is not allowed. However, ticket can be cancelled and full refund is admissible if the train is cancelled by Indian Railways."; 
	 public static String  sp_Block03_HeadingD04="     4.  For any reason, if berth cannot be given to passenger by Indian Railways on booked PNR, full refund shall be granted to the passenger through TDR.";
	 public static String  sp_Block03_HeadingD05="     5.  Agents will not be allowed to book tickets in trains with dynamic pricing."; 
	 
